<subSubSection id="B6DC9EABFFFCFFA6FC91748EDC3AFD22" pageId="77" pageNumber="90" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="FE79CD20FFFCFFA6FC91748EDC3AFD22" blockId="77.[794,1399,425,673]" pageId="77" pageNumber="90">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFFCFFA6FC91748EDBF1FE42" bold="true" box="[794,905,425,449]" pageId="77" pageNumber="90">Comment</emphasis>
: The original description of this species is based on 
<specimenCount id="E8C006A9FFFCFFA6FC0574EEDB89FE61" box="[910,1009,457,482]" pageId="77" pageNumber="90" type="generic" typeStatus="type">five type</specimenCount>
specimens from two localities in 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFFCFFA6FC9174CEDB1BFD82" box="[794,867,489,513]" name="Brunei" pageId="77" pageNumber="90">Brunei</collectingCountry>
and Sabah. The aedeagus of the above male resembles that illustrated by PACE (2008) for 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFFCFFA6FB79772EDD08FDA2" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2008" box="[1266,1392,521,545]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Amaurodera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="77" pageNumber="90" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="discoidea">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFFCFFA6FB79772EDD08FDA2" box="[1266,1392,521,545]" italics="true" pageId="77" pageNumber="90">A. discoidea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but the coloration slightly differs from that mentioned in the original description. 
<location id="FB199BFBFFFCFFA6FBAC776EDC1FFDE2" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:766F7C36FFFCFFA6FCB475D4DC3AFD22:FB199BFBFFFCFFA6FBAC776EDC1FFDE2" box="[1063,1127,585,609]" country="Brunei" name="Other" pageId="77" pageNumber="90">Other</location>
characters referred to in the original descriptions are irrelevant for an identification of 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFFCFFA6FCED77AEDC47FD22" box="[870,1087,649,673]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Amaurodera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="77" pageNumber="90" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFFCFFA6FCED77AEDB92FD22" box="[870,1002,649,673]" italics="true" pageId="77" pageNumber="90">Amaurodera</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
